  <lyrics>[V1]
 Alajjpachanquir suma Cristojj
 T'akhesiwaytawa.
 Cruzan ch'accatataw uñjastajj
 Juchanacajj laycu.
 :Jakenac khespiyaña munasajj
 Wilam wartawaytaw. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Janiw cunas a utjquituti
 Jumar pagañatac.
 Chuymajjaqui nayajj churjjsmajja
 Jumar sirviñatac.
 :Naya laycu t'akhesitamata
 Yuspagarapunsmaw. (Bis)
 
[V3]
 Take chekana parlasisqui
 Cruzan jiwatamat.
 Waljaniwa jakenacajja
 Jan catokapquiti.
 :Chuymanacaparojj parlamaya
 Cutt'aniñapatac.  (Bis)
 
 </lyrics></song>